BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 36 608 Td (Chapter 2: Understanding What AI Can Do) Tj ET
q 0.4 G 1 w 36 600 m 396 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 575 Td (AI is software that can learn, recognize patterns, and make decisions like a human would.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 553 Td (When you ask Siri a question, that is AI processing your voice and finding an answer.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 531 Td (When Netflix suggests a show you might like, that is AI learning your preferences.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 509 Td (AI is not a robot - it is the intelligence behind the apps and devices you already use.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 487 Td (AI can understand and generate human language, recognize faces, and predict what you need.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 465 Td (It gets better over time by learning from millions of interactions with people.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 443 Td (AI cannot feel emotions, but it can recognize and respond to yours appropriately.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 421 Td (Most AI tools are designed to be as simple as having a conversation.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 399 Td (You have probably already used AI without knowing it - search engines use AI constantly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 377 Td (The key is learning which AI tools solve your specific needs and desires.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 355 Td (Think of AI as a very smart assistant that never gets tired and is always available.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
