q 0.4 G 1 w 36 600 m 396 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 575 Td (As a grandparent, you play a key role in teaching digital wisdom to young ones.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 553 Td (Help grandchildren understand that not everything AI creates is true or accurate.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 531 Td (Teach them to verify AI-generated information with trusted sources.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 509 Td (Discuss privacy: explain why they should not share personal details with AI chatbots.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 487 Td (AI-generated images and videos \(deepfakes\) can look real but be completely fake.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 465 Td (Help them understand that AI should be a tool, not a replacement for critical thinking.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 443 Td (Set healthy boundaries around screen time and AI interaction for children.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 421 Td (Teach them that AI learns from what people put online - so be careful what you share.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 399 Td (Discuss how AI recommendations can create bubbles that limit perspectives.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 377 Td (Model healthy technology use yourself - showing balance is the best teaching tool.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 36 355 Td (Open conversations about AI build trust and keep communication flowing.) Tj ET

